OL,4,CCar production hit by 'pingdemic' and
OL,5,Cglobal chip shortage
OL,6, UK car production is still much lower
OL,7, than it needs to be due to shortages of
OL,8, staff and semiconductors, the industry
OL,9, is warning.
OL,11,FThe Society of Motor Manufacturers and
OL,12,FTraders (SMMT) said just 69,097 cars
OL,13,Fwere produced in June, the lowest since
OL,14,F1957, with the exception of last year.
OL,16,FThe trade body is calling for urgent
OL,17,Fassistance to exempt staff pinged by
OL,18,Fthe NHS Covid app.
OL,20,FSMMT said the industry was "desperately
OL,21,Ftrying to get back to full capacity".
